excerpt: Colorful waterside Colombia restaurant offering hearty comfort plates, seafood dishes & cocktails.
detail_description: La Regatta is a vibrant restaurant located by the waterside in Colombia, known for its hearty comfort plates, seafood dishes, and cocktails. It's a favorite among many for special occasions due to its high-quality food and top-notch service. The restaurant offers an experience even before dining, with a colorful pier adorned with local art and relics of a pirate ship. The menu features upscale options like hot garlic crab claws, lobster tail in bechamel, and conch in coconut sauce.
name: La Regatta
address: Cra. 1 #3 - 121, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Gourmet Shop Assho is a top-rated restaurant in San Andres, offering a blend of international and local cuisine with beautifully presented dishes. The menu features a variety of seafood, meat, and vegetarian options made with fresh island produce. Visitors have praised the warm and welcoming atmosphere as well as the high-quality dishes such as carrot soup, peppercorn steak, and shrimp and salmon salad.
name: Gourmet Shop Assho
address: 880001, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Capitán Mandy is a mid-range seafood restaurant located in San Andres Island, Colombia. It is known for its delicious Caribbean and Latin cuisine, offering a cozy atmosphere and exceptional service. The menu features recommended dishes such as fried fish and seafood. While the restaurant mainly focuses on seafood, it also offers limited vegetarian options like vegetarian rice and pasta with garlic and veggies. Visitors have praised the quality of the dishes considering the restaurant's specialty in seafood.
name: Capitán Mandy
address: #4b-2 a, Av Providencia #446, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: If you're looking for a delicious seafood meal, Donde Francesca should be your go-to choice. With both a full bar and outdoor seating, this restaurant is perfect for relaxing on the beach or enjoying live music in the evenings.
name: Donde Francesca
address: San Luis, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: If you're looking for a delightful culinary experience during your travels, Miss Celia Restaurante is a must-visit. Nestled close to the stunning beaches, this charming eatery offers an array of traditional Colombian dishes infused with modern flair. The ambiance captures the essence of the Caribbean, from its vibrant decor to the enticing aromas wafting from the kitchen, where specialties like snail stew are prepared with care.
name: Miss Celia Restaurante
address: Cl. 2, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Fisherman Place is a small, local beachside restaurant in San Andres Town that features fresh seafood. It's owned and operated by locals and can get busy, so be prepared to wait. The lobster is especially popular here and the view is fantastic.
name: Fisherman Place
address: Cra. 4 #2-37, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: The Islander is a popular restaurant known for its Caribbean-inspired fast food, particularly its seafood burgers like the shrimp burger. The menu also features wraps, tacos, and salads made with fresh, high-quality ingredients. Additionally, the restaurant offers a delightful breakfast menu. Located at Hotel Decameron Isleno, it's considered one of the best premium beachfront bars with excellent service and a diverse gastronomic selection. Visitors can enjoy a variety of dishes ranging from seafood to meat and poultry with tropical flavors.
name: The Islander
address: Cl. 1 #101 a 10-247, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Trattoria Mr. Panino is a surprising find on the small island of San Andres, offering delicious Italian cuisine. The menu includes a variety of options such as pasta, risotto, bruschetta, meats, seafood dishes, and sandwiches. Visitors have praised the generous portion sizes and recommended trying dishes like pasta al pesto and pasta carbonara. The restaurant also offers a selection of 49 food and drink items on its menu. Guests have highlighted the attentive service from friendly staff members.
name: Trattoria Mr. Panino
address: #2-2 a 2190 Calle 2, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Mahi Mahi is a restaurant located in the Casablanca Hotel, offering a Thai-themed dining experience. The restaurant provides a variety of menus including Italian, oriental, and international options. Customers can enjoy seafood dishes and other non-fish options such as vegetarian, red meat, or poultry. The atmosphere is pleasant with good decor and friendly service. While some visitors found the food to be just okay, others were pleasantly surprised by the flavorful dishes like chicken green curry and coconut curry.
name: Mahi Mahi
address: Cra. 4 #2-37, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

name: Restaurante Mari's Play
address: Cra. 1a #1147 #1-1 a, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

name: Restaurante y Bar Tico Tico
address: al lado de hotel calipso, Av peatonal, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Restaurante Niko’s Sea Food is a gem that captures the essence of Caribbean and Colombian seafood cuisine. Located in San Andres, it offers a delightful experience with its delectable seafood dishes. Despite its unassuming appearance, the restaurant boasts attentive and friendly staff who ensure a pleasant dining experience. Visitors can savor mouthwatering dishes such as salmon in garlic butter sauce or rice with shrimp while enjoying the warm hospitality of the staff.
name: Restaurante Niko’s Sea Food
address: Cl. 1 #1130 #1-2 a, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Restaurante el Parqueadero is a typical Colombian food spot located in downtown San Andres. It's known for its affordable prices and generous portions, making it popular among locals and travelers on a budget. The menu offers traditional Colombian dishes such as meatballs, fried pork, and caught of the day fried fish, all served with rice and salad. Despite some comments about slow service, many visitors appreciate the authentic experience and delicious food offered at this simple yet charming restaurant.
name: Restaurante el Parqueadero
address: Av. 20 De Julio, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Hamburguesas El Corral is a popular burger chain in Colombia that constantly evolves its menu to cater to new and demanding clientele. Despite its fast food vibe, the restaurant uses good quality ingredients, reflected in their reasonably priced meals. It's an ideal spot for a post-drinks snack or to enjoy the sunset with friendly service and a beachside view. The location offers a covered terrace for protection from the elements and accepts credit cards.
name: Hamburguesas El Corral
address: Av. Colombia #No. 1A -16, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Nestled in a vibrant spot on the island, Cafe Cafe Since 1992 is a delightful destination that combines a classy ambiance with an extensive cocktail menu and lively music. The rooftop deck offers stunning views of the stars and surrounding islands, making it perfect for evening relaxation. Known for its delicious pizza and friendly atmosphere, this cafe attracts both locals and visitors alike. The staff are incredibly welcoming, ensuring that every guest feels at home while enjoying their meals.
name: Cafe Cafe Since 1992
address: Avenida Colombia Edif Hansa Coral L 1 - 2 - 3, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

excerpt: Airy rooms, some with beach views, in a laid-back hotel offering open-air dining & an outdoor pool.
detail_description: Hotel Bahía Sardina is a laid-back hotel offering airy rooms, some with beach views, and open-air dining. It's located on the beautiful Spratt Bight beach in the north of San Andres Island, making it perfect for a vacation. The hotel features an outdoor pool and modern rooms with free Wi-Fi. With its proximity to the main sites in the center and a restaurant on-site, guests can enjoy convenience without having to walk far.
name: Hotel Bahía Sardina
address: Av. Colombia #5A-29, San Andrés, San Andres Islas, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Sunset Paradise is a family-run hotel where the owners take special care of their guests, even accommodating pets. Visitors appreciate the warm and helpful staff who go out of their way to make their stay enjoyable. The pet-friendly policy allows travelers to explore this destination with their furry companions, making it a highly recommended place for those seeking a welcoming and accommodating atmosphere.
name: Sunset Paradise
address: Barrio La Roccosa Kilometro 2, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Rocky Cay Restaurant Bar & Beach is a beachfront spot with abundant and shareable food, providing a nice break from the hustle of el Centro. The place offers good food in a beachy and pleasant setting right on the sand. Visitors can enjoy giant fish and great chicken dishes at reasonable prices. The staff is known for their excellent service and friendliness, making it the best option for those visiting Rocky Cay beach.
name: Rocky Cay Restaurant Bar & Beach
address: 01, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

name: Namaste Beach Club San Andres
address: G7VV+7R, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Kingston Jerk Spot is a must-visit for those craving Jamaican-style food in the Caribbean. While their Jerk Chicken is a standout, the pork and chicken curry are also highly recommended. The spot offers reasonably priced meals and has a small, cozy setting with about 5 tables. Visitors praise the delicious jerk sauce and generous portions served with rice, French fries, salad, and soup.
name: Kingston Jerk Spot
address: 01, San Luis, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

name: Booby Rock Ocean Club
address: 01, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Pollo kikiriki is a popular fast food option on the island, offering a simpler yet flavorful KFC-style fried chicken with good fries. The restaurant tends to be busy and may require some attention to table cleanliness, but the air conditioning is great. Visitors love the breaded fish dish served with a delicious cabbage salad, making it a favorite choice for many returning patrons. It's a great place to start off an evening of exploring local street food and the town area.
name: Pollo kikiriki
address: FRENTE A KIKIRIKI, Av. 20 De Julio, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: "RESTAURANTE NEXT TO THE BEACH" is a must-visit spot for a delightful dining experience on the island. The restaurant offers a variety of fresh and well-prepared dishes, including barracuda, pargo, and mojarra. Guests have praised the fair prices, delicious food, and friendly owner. The cozy atmosphere adds to the overall charm of the place.
name: Restaurante Next to The Beach
address: Av. Colombia, Carrera 1a #1-2a 1-41, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Mediterraneo Pizzeria & Sports Bar is a must-visit destination for sports enthusiasts and food lovers alike. Nestled on the island, this unique venue stands out as the only sports bar of its kind in the area. Not only can you catch your favorite games on multiple screens, but you can also indulge in some of Colombia's finest pizza, baked to perfection in a custom oven with a secret recipe that adds an air of mystery to each slice.
name: Mediterraneo Pizzeria & Sports Bar
address: Cra. 6 #1-100, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Beer Station in San Andrés is a popular spot offering American cuisine, fast food, and a bar. Located on Avenida Colombia 1a-16 Lc 102, it's known for its diverse menu featuring hamburgers, wings, ribs, chicken fingers, and hot dogs. The restaurant offers little tables for sharing where you can sample a variety of dishes. While the prices may seem high in Colombian pesos, they are quite affordable when compared to the euro.
name: Beer Station - San Andrés
address: Av. Colombia #55a1, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

excerpt: Modern beachfront hotel featuring multiple restaurants, plus free breakfast & an outdoor pool.
detail_description: Hotel Casablanca is a modern beachfront hotel located in San Andres, Colombia. It offers 91 rooms including standard double rooms, superior double rooms, and bungalows. The hotel features multiple restaurants and provides free breakfast to guests. With an outdoor pool and easy access to the nearby beach, it's strategically located just a short walk from downtown San Andres. Additionally, the hotel offers services such as car rental, business center facilities, and meeting rooms.
name: Hotel Casablanca
address: Av. Colombia #59, San Andrés, Islas, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Perú Wok - San Andrés offers a unique Peruvian culinary experience with a stunning sun terrace overlooking the endless sea and views of Johnny Cay. The restaurant serves delicious ceviche with mango and avocado, as well as other seafood dishes like rice and wok. Guests can enjoy good music at a pleasant volume while dining right by the water. Although the service could be improved, the quick food preparation and flavorful dishes make it worth a visit.
name: Perú Wok - San Andrés
address: Cl. 1 #1a-2 a #168, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Aqua Beach Club is a restaurant with a unique setting on the sea. It serves seafood and meat dishes, as well as vegetarian and vegan options. The restaurant has beautiful views of the ocean and it's open for lunch and brunch. Reservations are recommended, but there is usually seating available. It also has a full bar, so you can enjoy your meal to the fullest!
name: Aqua Beach Club
address: San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: La Pizzetta Florio is a renowned pizza restaurant in San Andres, Colombia, known for its wood-fired pizzas with a wide variety of fresh ingredients, including vegetarian and vegan options. Run by an Italian couple from Rome, the restaurant offers an authentic Italian atmosphere and delicious food. While some dishes like the bolognese and lasagna are highly recommended, others may not meet expectations. However, the standout items are the flavorful pizzas with excellent dough.
name: La Pizzetta Florio
address: A lado Banco de la Republica, centro comercial, Av. Colón, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Interstate 80s Food & Drinks is a restaurant that offers good and affordable food, along with a unique atmosphere and decor. The music played at the restaurant complements its theme, creating an enjoyable dining experience. The establishment also features an 80s-themed ambiance with music videos from that era playing on a screen. Additionally, there is a toy/gadget shop adjacent to the restaurant where visitors can purchase souvenirs.
name: Interstate 80s Food & Drinks
address: San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Bocca De Oro is a fantastic dining spot with amazing food and a lively atmosphere. The sauteed veggies are particularly noteworthy, offering a unique and delicious taste. Visitors can enjoy live reggae music while savoring dishes like the Picada Coco Loco, featuring Dorado fish and lobster. While the service may be a bit slow, it's friendly and accommodating.
name: Bocca De Oro
address: Cra. 1 #2252 2-58 a, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: El Paradise is a great beach restaurant with delicious seafood. It's casual but stylish, and the staff are friendly and helpful. You can enjoy drinks on the beach or grab lunch inside. The food is top quality, and the atmosphere is relaxed and comfortable.
name: Beach Restaurant the Paradise
address: San Andrés, San Luis, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: This restaurant serves Italian, Mexican, Latin, pizza and Colombian cuisine. Outdoor seating is available. Wheelchair access is available. Accepts American Express and Mastercard.
name: Restaurante Don Aníbal Col- Mex
address: Cl. 1 #1b21 #1b-7 a, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Sea Watch Caffe is a popular spot for breakfast and lunch, offering a variety of options from traditional American plates to delicious pancakes. The cafe is known for serving some of the best coffee on the island. While it may be slightly pricier than other similar restaurants, Sea Watch Caffe's beachfront location and air-conditioned seating make it worth the cost. In addition to their breakfast offerings, they also serve great pizzas, salads, and vegan options.
name: Sea Watch Caffe
address: Av. Colombia #3-59, San Andrés, Islas, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Restaurante Punta Sur is a must-visit for those craving Latin American seafood cuisine. Located at the southeastern tip of the island, it offers a picturesque Caribbean backdrop with a terrace resembling a ship's bow overlooking the sea. The restaurant's attention to detail is evident in its wooden and stone decorations. While there may not be vegetarian options, visitors can enjoy fresh and delicious seafood dishes like fish casserole.
name: Restaurante Punta Sur
address: San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

excerpt: Pizza, ceviches & Angus burgers offered in a colorful, casual restaurant with outdoor seating.
detail_description: Seaweed is a casual restaurant with outdoor seating that serves pizza, ceviches, and Angus burgers. It is colorful and full of atmosphere, with a lively feel that will make you want to come back for more. The menu features a variety of Latin and Caribbean dishes as well as seafood options, making it the perfect spot for anyone looking for something different. Late night hours are also available if you're looking to get your grub on afterhours.
name: Seaweed
address: a 4b-116, Cra. 1 #4b-2, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: The restaurant Aquarius Bar serves up some of the most delicious seafood you'll ever taste. The cazuela de mariscos is a dish that combines the spices of Nicaragua and Colombia, resulting in an amazing flavor experience. If you're looking for a delicious seafood meal, be sure to check out Aquarius Bar!
name: Restaurante Aquarius Bar
address: Cra. 6 #1-100, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: EL PERUANO is a highly recommended restaurant located in front of Spratt Bight, offering a fusion of Colombian and Peruvian cuisine. While it's considered one of the more expensive dining options on the island, visitors praise its delicious food and stunning views. The menu features fresh ceviche, flavorful arroz chaufa de mariscos, and well-prepared calamares apanados.
name: EL PERUANO
address: Cl. 3 #5-12, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Qbano is a charming restaurant that offers a taste of Cuban cuisine in a vibrant and welcoming setting. The menu features a variety of traditional Cuban dishes, including flavorful meats, hearty stews, and tasty side dishes. The restaurant's lively atmosphere and friendly staff create an authentic experience for diners looking to explore the flavors of Cuba. Whether you're craving classic Cuban sandwiches or want to try some delicious plantains, Qbano has something for everyone.
name: Qbano
address: Av. 20 De Julio #11-09, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: If you find yourself in San Andres and are on the hunt for a dining experience that combines both exceptional food and attentive service, look no further than El Rincón de la Langosta Centro. This charming eatery stands out as a true gem amidst the culinary landscape of the island. Guests rave about their delectable seafood offerings, including standout dishes like lobster tail and cazuela de mariscos, which have garnered high praise from locals and visitors alike.
name: El Rincón de la Langosta Centro
address: Iglesia Cristo Salvador, Cl. 2 #1b frente a, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Rosa Del Mar is a charming eatery known for its delectable seafood tacos and refreshing juices. While some visitors have noted that the service can be leisurely, it's all part of the laid-back island atmosphere that blends seamlessly with Colombian time. The establishment comes highly recommended for those looking to savor excellent fish tacos and enjoy a relaxed dining experience with top-notch service.
name: Rosa Del Mar
address: San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Shima Sushi Cafe Bar offers a delightful shrimp tom yum soup that is perfect for a rainy day, with just the right amount of spiciness to give it an extra kick. However, their pad thai dish may not be the best choice as it was described as sour and salty instead of the expected sweet savory flavor. On the bright side, their sushi is highly praised for its amazing quality and variety. The bar also serves wonderful cocktails and provides good service.
name: Shima Sushi cafe Bar
address: carrera 1-# 2-2 punta Hansa, punta Hansa, centro comercial arena Blanca, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: EatAlley is a trendy Italian and Colombian restaurant tucked away in an alley, offering a delightful dining experience under the glow of string lights. The menu features reasonably priced 25-ish cm pizzas and flavorful pasta dishes. Diners can enjoy outdoor seating and modify their pizzas for vegetarian options. Despite some wait times, the quality of the food makes it worth it.
name: EatAlley
address: 01 #2-189 a 2-1, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Bibi's place is a charming spot located on San Andres, accessible only by boat. It offers a delightful dining experience with its well-cooked and fresh seafood dishes, such as the flavorful fish fillet served with rice, salad, and frutipan. Visitors praise the excellent quality of the food and the unbeatable views at this 100% touristic destination. While some mention disorganized service, others highlight the friendly atmosphere and Bibi's warm personality.
name: Bibi's place
address: H826+7M, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Rest. Terraza Portobelo is a great place to have a meal, whether you're looking for breakfast, lunch, or dinner. The food is delicious and the prices are reasonable, making it a great choice for both tourists and locals alike. The service can be a bit slow at times, but the restaurant itself is spacious and nicely decorated. Plus, there's plenty of seating so you can relax and enjoy your meal.
name: Rest. Terraza Portobelo
address: Hotel portobelo, San Andrés, Isla de San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Stars Kitchen is a lovely beachside spot with a welcoming atmosphere and attentive staff. It's the kind of place where you can relax without feeling pressured to constantly order drinks.
name: Stars Kitchen
address: San Luis, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Rest. Jeno's Pizza offers a positive overall experience with good service and acceptable pizza flavors, despite not being as sophisticated as fast-food pizza chains. The option to choose half-and-half toppings on one pizza is a plus, allowing customers to enjoy different flavors in one order. The prices are relatively affordable compared to other dining options on the island. However, some customers experienced longer wait times for their orders and found the restaurant atmosphere noisy and not conducive to quiet family dinners.
name: Rest. Jeno's Pizza
address: Cl. 3 #5-12, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: Restaurante Pelicano is a popular dining spot where visitors can enjoy a delightful meal. The seafood stew and fried tilapia are among the standout dishes, served alongside fresh salad and rice. Guests appreciate the prompt service and the delectable, piping hot food. With its reputation for offering affordable and delicious meals, it's no wonder that many consider it to be an excellent choice for daily lunch outings.
name: Restaurante Pelicano
address: Cra. 4 #2-37, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

name: Da Vanni Trattoria
address: a 1a-67, Cl. 1 #1a-1, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia

detail_description: PAVAROTTI TAPAS & PIZZA is a charming spot conveniently located near the BnB, making it an ideal choice for solo travelers looking to explore the area. The friendly staff are accommodating and helpful, especially for those not fluent in Spanish. The menu offers a variety of delectable options such as fish salad, rice, quinoa bowls with warm veggies, and focaccia with veggies.
name: PAVAROTTI TAPAS & PIZZA
address: Edif Telefónica, Cl. 4 #2 A - 61, San Andrés, San Andrés y Providencia, Colombia
